♪That light keeps me strong
in my solitude♪

195
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,470
By the way,

196
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,560
I wanted to tell you

197
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:11,150
that I've been having
weird dreams lately.

198
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:14,750
I dreamt I arrived in the Great Yan,

199
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,720
where there was a cold-faced prince
named Su Qianyu.

200
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:25,630
Then it seemed I swapped
bodies with that prince.

201
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:28,720
I became him, and he became me.

202
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:34,120
The first time we swapped,

203
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,840
and the second time we switched back.

204
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,510
Isn't that strange?

205
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:41,820
Though it's quite strange,

206
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,700
I'm still very happy
that you are in my dreams.

207
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,320
And then?

208
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:58,720
And then? Of course,
I haven't dreamed of it.

209
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,720
But if it's a happy ending,

210
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,600
I will tell you.

211
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:07,850
It'll definitely be a happy ending.

212
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:38,850
♪Gazing at distant mountains far away♪

213
00:12:39,290 --> 00:12:42,140
♪Waiting for the peach blossoms
to bloom on the branches♪

214
00:12:42,540 --> 00:12:47,080
♪With petals falling on the balcony,
you step into the morning glow♪

215
00:12:48,930 --> 00:12:51,850
♪Painting a scroll
of splendid mountains and seas♪

216
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:55,060
♪In the depths of the clouds,
leaving space for you♪

217
00:12:55,460 --> 00:13:00,790
♪Wandering together,
no need to wait any longer♪

218
